      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NCWidgetController"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class defines an object that both a Today widget and the containing app that delivers the widget can use to specify whether the widget has content to display. Because this class helps a widget and its containing app coordinate the display of the widget’s content, a widget that doesn’t communicate with its containing app is unlikely to use this class."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Typically, a widget appears in the Today view when it has content to display. If a currently running widget no longer has content to display, it can get a widget controller and set the flag in the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/notificationcenter/ncwidgetcontroller/1456693-sethascontent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method to "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "false"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If the containing app later determines that there is content this widget should display, the app can get a widget controller and update the flag, even while the widget isn’t running."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NCWidgetController"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class should not be subclassed."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
